Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está esperando?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Destrua o núcleo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Placenta invadiu o\Ncockpit do esqueleto de Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.12,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é uma Hoshijiro Shizuka reciclada\Npor Benisuzume a partir de placenta.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Não deveria ter sido permitido entrar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0].
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Você nos ouve?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.32,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos fechando o bloqueio na nuca\Nque cortará a placenta invasora!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Izana...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tem que desconectar a unidade da cabeça!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,O pulso de Nagate está aumentando.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O esqueleto perdeu o poder.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauna,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}pare de nos imitar...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Hoshijiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Como estamos indo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou quase lá!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Não podemos fazer isso, Shinatose.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas um pouco mais!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos fazer isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou conectado!
