Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Hoshijiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:04.93,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}100 Atrações de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.93,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Descida e Pousada do Hayakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:04.93,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Laboratório Subterrâneo Ochiai, Jardim Verde
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós estamos em órbita ao redor do Planeta Nove.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,E o grande ninho?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem alteração.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que ganhamos um tempinho de descanso.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora não há volta atrás.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.41,0:16:30.17,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Sidonia conseguiu entrar na órbita do Planeta Nove hoje.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.63,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,O Planeta Nove é abençoado com recursos abundantes,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.05,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,e seus anéis externos podem ser usados como fortificação natural,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.05,0:16:42.68,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,então o quartel-general está confiante que {\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}desse ponto de operações...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que agora não há volta atrás.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.02,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Em breve, um sonho de há uma centena de anos [T2]virá a frutificar.[T3]
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meu{\i0} sonho.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnação como uma forma de vida superior.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Em reconhecimento ao seu valor\Ndurante a conquista do Planeta Nove
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,nós lhe concedemos o\NOrdem da Formação de Oito-Quadros.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é um verdadeiro cavaleiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostra-me o seu medalhão.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Ren.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Não estás sendo um pouco insistente?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.12,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso não é da sua conta, En.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Parabéns, Tanikaze Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu espero grandes coisas de você.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho também suas graças.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por resgatar Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Hoshijiro—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Quero dizer, onde está o placentário?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos cuidando disso\Ncomo uma espécime valiosa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Tudo bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.87,0:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Coisas importantes devem ter um respaldo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.97,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não demos medalhas a ninguém há décadas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.68,0:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que isso motiva os pilotos a lutar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare de usá-lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos você é?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.03,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Os corações dos homens são frágeis.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.29,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,É desanimador lutar sem sob a bandeira do herói a que nos unirmos.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deve saber isso como eu sei.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou em casa...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.15,0:19:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o primeiro aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:07.33,Box,,0,0,0,,{\c&H74CAEA&\3c&H6FC4F0&\blur2\pos(978,320)}Instant\N Ramen Gravitacional
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:07.33,Box,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H6FC4F0&\pos(978,326)\c&H433F42&\blur1}Instant\N Ramen de Gravidade
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-HO...! H-H-HOT! QUENTE! QUENTE...!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunca faça isso novamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O que? O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te ajudarei a se desculpar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,E não se preocupe,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate nunca poderia te odiar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Você realmente acha isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.83,0:21:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.07,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas por ter usado seu uniforme sem permissão.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, não chore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.29,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não sabia que você podia fazer isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas... por que você escolheu Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.45,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,É porque...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.47,0:22:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze se culpa pela morte de Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.71,0:22:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele tem lutado com a culpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.19,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,se eu parecesse com Hoshijiro e lhe dissesse que não era sua culpa...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ele se sentiria melhor.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.47,0:22:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.43,0:22:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,foi realmente doloroso para Tanikaze lutar contra Benisuzume.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.59,0:22:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.11,0:22:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.03,0:22:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deveria ter sido doloroso para você também...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.03,0:22:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...lutar contra Benisuzume, também.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.89,0:22:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.19,0:22:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.67,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, vocês dois!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.53,0:23:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze... Eu...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas por ter gritado com vocês.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.49,0:23:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, encontrei um food stand automatizado por aqui perto que vocês devem conseguir alcançar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.51,0:23:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Vocês dois querem verificar?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.57,0:23:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.51,0:23:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem. Na verdade, ainda não comi nada essa semana.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.91,0:23:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Está bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é divertido.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.07,0:23:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é o Piloto Tanikaze Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.41,0:23:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Olá de novo.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.63,0:23:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, eu realmente me desculpo por isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, se sinta em casa. Vou servir um chá para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.41,0:24:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, não há problema.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.61,0:24:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava a caminho de algum lugar.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.95,0:24:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.85,0:24:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Volte sempre.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.71,0:24:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou pedir um arrozado para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.77,0:24:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta é a sala onde você foi admitido pela primeira vez.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.15,0:24:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso acreditar que o ladrão de arroz virou Piloto Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.15,0:24:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, desculpe.\NI não precisava ter levantado esse assunto.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.93,0:25:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas pelo incômodo\NI causei a você.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.39,0:25:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, você não precisa se desculpar por isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.82,0:25:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.70,0:25:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo lá?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:30.67,0:25:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,É você!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.21,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Piloto Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.71,0:25:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.67,0:25:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Permissão de Entrada...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.05,0:25:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.92,0:25:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Você quer ver sua casa.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.47,0:25:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.35,0:25:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:53.65,0:25:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leve isso consigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.98,0:25:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
