Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.98,0:26:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas fico feliz em ter saído.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.58,0:26:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Muitas coisas aconteceram comigo.{\i0}
