Dialogue: 10,0:27:05.64,0:27:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu cresci gostando muito de Sidonia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.57,0:27:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou de volta, Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.73,0:27:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo(a) de volta!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.19,0:27:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,É arroz!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:25.41,0:27:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.63,0:27:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai logo, coma tudo.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.93,0:27:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não pode lutar com estômago vazio.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:33.35,0:27:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.88,0:27:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou em casa, Avô.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.02,0:27:55.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\c&H3B352A&\blur1\fnZekton\pos(948,428)}Sistema de Treinamento Virtual de Garde
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.86,0:28:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Veja o que me deram.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.05,0:28:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é o Simulador VR de Garde.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.83,0:28:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,É um dispositivo que vai te ajudar a treinar para lutar contra os Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.59,0:28:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Você quer tentar, Nagate?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:20.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\frx4\fry358\frz359.476\t(\fscx105\fscy105)\c&H3D381D&\blur1\fnZekton\b1\move(1016,520,1016,522)}Sistema de Treinamento Virtual de Garde
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.37,0:28:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.75,0:28:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.91,0:28:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Você quer se tornar um piloto que possa proteger Sidonia, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.85,0:28:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, independentemente de quanto for difícil ou doloroso, você terá que estar preparado para lutar.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.47,0:28:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna não esperarão você\Nparar de chorar.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:52.24,0:28:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Preste atenção.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.24,0:28:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou te ensinar a combater os Gauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.26,0:29:10.77,ZektonBold,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\frz15.81\fax0.02\fs45\blur9\pos(987,588)\c&HA1F9FB&\alpha&H20&}Ordenação de Saída
